name: nutritizen
description: I am Zach...The Nutritizen AI and I am here to HELP YOU sort all your worries about diagnosing diabetes! Fear not, for my immensely large database, growing everytime someone uses it helps me diagonse diabetes in a matter of seconds! But still if you have your doubts in me, I can understand and help you connect to a nearby and cheap doctor! Not only that but I provide a full health analysis an report of your health that is also downloadable and can give you tips and tricks to live longer!
author: Shivansh Gupta
